{"tid":578600,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好難觸摸呀","createTime":"2018-03-02T18:04:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-03T14:56:07.000Z","uid":147988,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0467b946a207d5afb5fcfa9a892066509983228c","tid":578600,"uid":147988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T18:04:50.000Z","msg":"男朋友一返工就會無左影，覆唔到機，呢個真心明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n放工佢會攰，我都知。<br />\n佢返早的話放工就去睇下玩具，返屋企食飯咁，食完飯隨時攰到唔小心瞓著左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n收夜就更加啦 有時我都瞓左<br />\n而佢覆機真係好慢，短則隔10幾分鐘覆一次，長則隔個幾兩個鐘都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁計計落落，一日講到十句野已經叫正常。我地都好少會whatsapp講果日發生咩事，一黎佢可能無呢個習慣佢唔會咩都同我講，二黎我知佢攰費事講咁多野要佢聽，我都知佢無心機覆。咁唔講呢啲，平日whatsapp講野就顯得好冷清，講既野好形式化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時佢會po下啲cap圖上story，見佢同朋友講野又可以好快覆到日講夜講果啲。其實果下心理又會唔平衡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就係靠一個禮拜見一次咁傾個計，見面既時候都好正常架，但見完又要再loop過呢個過程<br />\n呼 其實好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁相處是咪正常，其實明明大家都返緊工，但點解感覺大家個世界都好唔同咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁耐以黎我都睇唔透到底係點解<br />\n好想知返緊工既你地平時點同另一半維繫感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36da7e443e0406e174a779d98073c11dfca5f466","tid":578600,"uid":170867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T18:06:40.000Z","msg":"試下等佢收工個陣陪佢睇下玩具"},{"pid":"8355ef4fc21534f26c406e802d12ff52169db71f","tid":578600,"uid":109220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0467b946a207d5afb5fcfa9a892066509983228c","tid":578600,"uid":147988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T18:04:50.000Z","msg":"男朋友一返工就會無左影，覆唔到機，呢個真心明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n放工佢會攰，我都知。<br />\n佢返早的話放工就去睇下玩具，返屋企食飯咁，食完飯隨時攰到唔小心瞓著左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n收夜就更加啦 有時我都瞓左<br />\n而佢覆機真係好慢，短則隔10幾分鐘覆一次，長則隔個幾兩個鐘都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁計計落落，一日講到十句野已經叫正常。我地都好少會whatsapp講果日發生咩事，一黎佢可能無呢個習慣佢唔會咩都同我講，二黎我知佢攰費事講咁多野要佢聽，我都知佢無心機覆。咁唔講呢啲，平日whatsapp講野就顯得好冷清，講既野好形式化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時佢會po下啲cap圖上story，見佢同朋友講野又可以好快覆到日講夜講果啲。其實果下心理又會唔平衡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就係靠一個禮拜見一次咁傾個計，見面既時候都好正常架，但見完又要再loop過呢個過程<br />\n呼 其實好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁相處是咪正常，其實明明大家都返緊工，但點解感覺大家個世界都好唔同咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁耐以黎我都睇唔透到底係點解<br />\n好想知返緊工既你地平時點同另一半維繫感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T18:09:17.000Z","msg":"一齊咗幾耐呀樓主？"},{"pid":"cfe1f56bfe18c413770f08a66fc1943970c27a50","tid":578600,"uid":147988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T18:11:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試下等佢收工個陣陪佢睇下玩具</blockquote><br />\n有時佢會一支箭咁飛左去，自己睇完就走<br />\n覆得慢到，佢話完去睇玩具，我問佢係邊我過去搵佢，佢再答就話睇完啦咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bb6d50b654fc03ed0cf9e7c2899f0712a77a5b5","tid":578600,"uid":147988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T18:11:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>男朋友一返工就會無左影，覆唔到機，呢個真心明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n放工佢會攰，我都知。<br />\n佢返早的話放工就去睇下玩具，返屋企食飯咁，食完飯隨時攰到唔小心瞓著左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n收夜就更加啦 有時我都瞓左<br />\n而佢覆機真係好慢，短則隔10幾分鐘覆一次，長則隔個幾兩個鐘都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁計計落落，一日講到十句野已經叫正常。我地都好少會whatsapp講果日發生咩事，一黎佢可能無呢個習慣佢唔會咩都同我講，二黎我知佢攰費事講咁多野要佢聽，我都知佢無心機覆。咁唔講呢啲，平日whatsapp講野就顯得好冷清，講既野好形式化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時佢會po下啲cap圖上story，見佢同朋友講野又可以好快覆到日講夜講果啲。其實果下心理又會唔平衡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就係靠一個禮拜見一次咁傾個計，見面既時候都好正常架，但見完又要再loop過呢個過程<br />\n呼 其實好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁相處是咪正常，其實明明大家都返緊工，但點解感覺大家個世界都好唔同咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁耐以黎我都睇唔透到底係點解<br />\n好想知返緊工既你地平時點同另一半維繫感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>一齊咗幾耐呀樓主？</blockquote><br />\n兩年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fd0be979451f34f3ac0c125b09b124fa831bb63","tid":578600,"uid":170867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfe1f56bfe18c413770f08a66fc1943970c27a50","tid":578600,"uid":147988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T18:11:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試下等佢收工個陣陪佢睇下玩具</blockquote><br />\n有時佢會一支箭咁飛左去，自己睇完就走<br />\n覆得慢到，佢話完去睇玩具，我問佢係邊我過去搵佢，佢再答就話睇完啦咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T18:14:48.000Z","msg":"咁不如你地搵幾日係出面食埋夜晚啦 佢咁急返去有野做定點"},{"pid":"e59f7939ffc278b641857ca70e0f2780c264641f","tid":578600,"uid":147988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T18:22:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>試下等佢收工個陣陪佢睇下玩具</blockquote><br />\n有時佢會一支箭咁飛左去，自己睇完就走<br />\n覆得慢到，佢話完去睇玩具，我問佢係邊我過去搵佢，佢再答就話睇完啦咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>咁不如你地搵幾日係出面食埋夜晚啦 佢咁急返去有野做定點</blockquote><br />\n一係收工話攰，一係約左人(佢都真係幾多約<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )，再唔係佢就話想返屋企食住家飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93b2e71eb18646b74649732409b2acbfa118d33b","tid":578600,"uid":169807,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T23:17:41.000Z","msg":"一齊住未唔駛咁煩lor"},{"pid":"b6ba1bf337f73ad8c664176f2a6633f811f1e36a","tid":578600,"uid":15823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T23:21:59.000Z","msg":"兩年都忍到好快80歲架喇"},{"pid":"9d5492d00b52ebf082acbba60556cc4064ba58b6","tid":578600,"uid":26971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T23:35:08.000Z","msg":"一直係咁都忍到都唔差在忍埋下半世啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"670f13320956eb1e8a85c60c2b474fac2faeeda8","tid":578600,"uid":132478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T23:55:58.000Z","msg":"試下唔理佢 睇下佢有咩反應<br />\n如果佢都唔care<br />\n咁分得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09d3d50fa40f9cb27b53f7bd41c3bb4183856789","tid":578600,"uid":147988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T03:53:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一直係咁都忍到都唔差在忍埋下半世啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都希望自己真係忍到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8c9f11071dfb7d42f3fbe22e505eb794e3f2863","tid":578600,"uid":147988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T03:53:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩年都忍到好快80歲架喇</blockquote><br />\n就係忍唔到 中間都有分過手<br />\n但大家都離唔開大家又一齊返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85f8588756ad2d275ce0d16d735c3ca19f5c0acd","tid":578600,"uid":147988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T03:56:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試下唔理佢 睇下佢有咩反應<br />\n如果佢都唔care<br />\n咁分得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試過 唔理佢咪又主動撩下你 約返你囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當你以爲佢對你上心既時候 自己無意中又會主動左 佢咪又打回原形<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df43e0e3f5430f0663c8e11a2eb36b0b5218a16e","tid":578600,"uid":30710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T03:58:57.000Z","msg":"同男朋友一齊就半年 朝朝早都會講早晨然後傾幾句，跟住就做嘢<br />\n佢返工都比較忙所以通常佢都會交低聲話「做嘢先」「準備開會」然後無咗影幾個鐘之後放工果時又出現返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時真係得閒放到工大家就會約放工出嚟食個飯陪佢睇吓玩具咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 陪佢睇玩具都幾開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n絲打可以試吓同男友提出下"},{"pid":"54be3c39fbe2730c3013e89090d0574dfad82851","tid":578600,"uid":30710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T04:01:51.000Z","msg":"而放假通常大家禮拜六都會見 禮拜日就會用嚟休息唔出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但大家想見都會見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d87cc1204210a86e5ee0ca7b963390e0b68fd50a","tid":578600,"uid":147988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T04:59:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同男朋友一齊就半年 朝朝早都會講早晨然後傾幾句，跟住就做嘢<br />\n佢返工都比較忙所以通常佢都會交低聲話「做嘢先」「準備開會」然後無咗影幾個鐘之後放工果時又出現返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時真係得閒放到工大家就會約放工出嚟食個飯陪佢睇吓玩具咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 陪佢睇玩具都幾開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n絲打可以試吓同男友提出下</blockquote><br />\n佢份人好獨立 獨立到想做咩就即刻自己去做左先<br />\n我永遠都係被通知 想陪都陪唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢都可以放工出現返就好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4de2be3c92f7e7d1dfedbe508a5df483743d0d79","tid":578600,"uid":118455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T04:59:47.000Z","msg":"幫佢出火咪得"},{"pid":"14e3a202cfbd07c793f6cf664d88e1cca67cae8d","tid":578600,"uid":147988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T05:01:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幫佢出火咪得</blockquote><br />\n忙到無時間出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢見朋友仲多過見我"},{"pid":"f4333b018fb6c2705592e2fbe1b72647f84a38a8","tid":578600,"uid":118455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14e3a202cfbd07c793f6cf664d88e1cca67cae8d","tid":578600,"uid":147988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T05:01:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幫佢出火咪得</blockquote><br />\n忙到無時間出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢見朋友仲多過見我"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T05:07:51.000Z","msg":"屌厭左你姐"},{"pid":"529b88ac7dd8b28023be298b41b1ea93cd89af7e","tid":578600,"uid":147988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T05:20:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>幫佢出火咪得</blockquote><br />\n忙到無時間出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢見朋友仲多過見我</blockquote>屌厭左你姐</blockquote><br />\n無扑過野 何來厭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35e53c04c5e869ffb5c25998304dc7d7af156b1b","tid":578600,"uid":118455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"529b88ac7dd8b28023be298b41b1ea93cd89af7e","tid":578600,"uid":147988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T05:20:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>幫佢出火咪得</blockquote><br />\n忙到無時間出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢見朋友仲多過見我</blockquote>屌厭左你姐</blockquote><br />\n無扑過野 何來厭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T05:32:57.000Z","msg":"味朴都咁好可能佢都係唔想冇拖拍先同你一齊 利申 從男人角度分析"},{"pid":"4a96f003bb4c5e2d108ae2c977154742342f08b4","tid":578600,"uid":159002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T05:42:33.000Z","msg":"邊一個發明了返工<br />\n返工返到個人拍拖既心力同時間都少左好多"},{"pid":"b3ac9aeb603ed3b4bfdd0f3cc9794cf938743672","tid":578600,"uid":132478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quo